# Security and Money Review Gates

- Enforce strict auth and role checks for all write actions.
- Never use floating-point math for money paths.
- Keep tenant and location scoping explicit in reads and writes.

## Mandatory Human Review

Do not treat these as auto-merge safe. Require human senior-dev review for changes touching:

- money calculations or money schema
- payroll logic and exports
- inventory reorder formulas
- auth, policy, or permission logic
- tenant/location scoping logic
- data migrations that transform business data

## Safe Change Pattern

- Include risk level (low/medium/high) in PR or handoff notes.
- Include test evidence and rollback approach for high-risk changes.
